Package: modulr
Title: Simulate modular fission-fusion networks and sample design
Version: 0.8.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Gavin", "Cotterill", , "gcotterill2@unl.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1408-778X"))
Description: '`modulr` provides functions to simulate group switching behavior and create weighted, undirected social networks based on the proportion of time dyads spend together. `modulr` also simulates sampling processes and gives users to the tools to assess network statistic estimation under diverse scenarios'.
